      <h3>LPG Reach Truck</h3>
      <p>Can work outdoor too. Stronger power. Good for cold storage (works in low temps).</p>

      <h3>Stand-Up Reach Truck</h3>
      <p>Operator stands up. Good for fast moves. Best when getting on and off often.</p>

      <h3>Sit-Down Reach Truck</h3>
      <p>Operator sits down. Good for long shifts. More comfortable for all-day work.</p>

